<div class="banner" style="background-image: url(https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1504006833117-8886a355efbf?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjEyMDd9&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1650&q=80)">
  <div class=banner-container>
    <h1>Welcome to <em>Scurious</em></h1>
    <br><br><br><br>
    <div class="slogan">
      <h4>where curiosity <em>pushes</em> ideas <br> to become reality.</h4>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container">

  <h2 class="text-center">Here, we gather three kind of Scurious people : </h2>

  <div class="cards flex-wrap d-flex justify-content-around">
    <div class="card">
      <img src="https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2017/06/10/07/21/chat-2389223_1280.png" alt="">
      <h4>Idea generator</h4>
      <p>"I have a dream" is what you keep thinking ?<br>
      <% if current_user %>
        <% if current_user.role == "creator" %>
          <%= link_to " Share it here ", new_project_path %>
        <% else %>
          They share it here
        <% end %>
      <% else %>
        They share it here
      <% end %>
      to make it real 🌿</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <img src="https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2017/03/08/14/20/flat-2126876_1280.png" alt="">
      <h4>Developer</h4>
      <p>Pratice makes perfect and you want to thrive into your code ?<br>Find projects 🚀</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <img src="https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2014/04/02/16/20/lemon-306958_1280.png" alt="">
      <h4>Angel Investor</h4>
      <p>What's best than investing money into fruitful ideas, it's<br>juicy here! 🍋 </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="projects-container text-center">
  <%= simple_form_for :search, url: root_path, method: :get do |f| %>
    <div id="search-data" class="search-form-control form-group mx-5">
      <input class="form-control string required text-center" id="search-input" type="text" name="search[query]" placeholder="Search a project here!" />
    </div>
  <% end %>

  <div class="cards cards-results flex-wrap d-flex justify-content-center">

    <% @projects.each do |project| %>
      <%= render partial: 'projectcard', locals: { project: project } %>
    <% end %>

  </div>
  <% if current_user %>
    <% if current_user.role == "creator" %>
      <div class="text-center">
        <%= link_to " Share a new project ", new_project_path, class: 'btn btn-new' %>
      </div>
    <% end %>
  <% end %>
</div>

   <div class="bottom-page text-center">
    <%= link_to 'Back to the top', root_path, class: 'btn btn-menu' %>
  </div>
</div>
